<body>
<div type="writingSession">
<pb n="1"/>
<opener>
<salute>Lieber Herr <rs ref="#tillich_person_id__1783" type="person">Siegfried</rs>!</salute>
</opener>
    <p>Ich werde tun, was ich kann, wenn ich Ende dieser Woche in <rs ref="#tillich_place_id__37" type="place">Berlin</rs> bin.</p>
    <closer><salute>Herzliche Grüsse<lb/>
    In Eile Ihr</salute>
<signed><rs ref="#tillich_person_id__1928" type="person">P. Tillich</rs>.</signed>
</closer>    
</div>
